939. Am Heart J. 1984 Sep;108(3 Pt 2):794-6. doi: 10.1016/0002-8703(84)90673-2.

Coronary heart disease mortality/morbidity and risk in blacks. II: Access to 
medical care.

Haywood LJ.

Since the cardiovascular disease mortality is higher, life expectancy shorter, 
